snippet.title: Ni no Kuni II: Revenant Kingdom - Prince’s Edition | Xbox Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the story of a boy who becomes a true king.

Ni No Kuni II: Revenant Kingdom [Prince’s Edition] is now available on Xbox Game Pass, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and Windows PC – including all DLCs!

Get the game here: https://bnent.eu/NNK2Buy
